## Workflow

Bobby uses a ticket-based workflow with these stages:

```
0-ideas → 1-backlog → 2-ready-for-refinement → 3-ready-for-development
→ 4-in-progress → 5-ready-for-review → 6-ready-for-testing
→ 7-ready-for-release → 10-released
```

Side tracks: `8-needs-rework`, `9-blocked`

## Roles

### Engineer (bobby-build skill)
When told to "work tickets" or "bobby build", load the `bobby-build` skill from `.claude/skills/bobby-build/SKILL.md`. This skill handles:
- Picking up tickets from `3-ready-for-development`
- TDD red-green-refactor cycle
- Running health checks before/after changes
- Moving tickets through the pipeline

### QE (bobby-test skill)
When told to "test tickets" or "bobby test", load the `bobby-test` skill from `.claude/skills/bobby-test/SKILL.md`. This handles:
- Testing tickets in `6-ready-for-testing`
- Browser-based verification
- Writing QE notes with evidence

### Peer Reviewer (bobby-review skill)
When told to "review tickets" or "bobby review", load the `bobby-review` skill from `.claude/skills/bobby-review/SKILL.md`.

### Refiner (bobby-refine skill)
When told to "refine tickets" or "bobby refine", load the `bobby-refine` skill from `.claude/skills/bobby-refine/SKILL.md`.

### Release Engineer (bobby-release skill)
When told to "release tickets" or "bobby release", load the `bobby-release` skill from `.claude/skills/bobby-release/SKILL.md`.

### Ideator (bobby-ideate skill)
When told to "ideate", "brainstorm", or "bobby ideate", load the `bobby-ideate` skill from `.claude/skills/bobby-ideate/SKILL.md`.

## Learnings

Each skill has a `learnings.md` file that accumulates anti-patterns and best practices discovered during development. Always check the learnings file before starting work — it contains hard-won wisdom from past mistakes.

## Bobby CLI Commands

```
bobby create -t "Title" --type bug -p high   # Create ticket
bobby list                                    # Show board
bobby start TKT-001                          # Pick up ticket
bobby review TKT-001                         # Submit for review
bobby approve TKT-001                        # QE approve
bobby release TKT-001                        # Ship it
bobby retro TKT-001 "pattern name"           # Create retrospective
bobby learn bobby-build "pattern" "desc"     # Add learning
```
